AFC Women's Awards Conferred on DPRK Team and Footballers
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, November 8 (KCNA) -- The awards of the Asian Football Confederation (AFC) were conferred on the DPRK women's football team and footballers at the First AFC Women's Awards Ceremony 2007 held in Malaysia on November 6. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The DPRK Women's Football Team, which displayed a high degree of ability in several women's football tournaments held this year, won the AFC National Women's Team of the year award. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The AFC Women's Player of the year award was given to footballer Ri Kum Suk who played core role of her team in the Fifth FIFA Women's World Cup and scored 12 goals in the Asian regional women's football qualifiers for the 29th Olympic Games. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Footballer Ra Un Sim was honored with the AFC Women's Youth Player of the year award. She made a great contribution to the DPRK youth women's team which won the 2007 Asian Women's U-19 Football Championships held in China some time ago. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The DPRK is the first in the number of award winners at the First AFC Women's Awards Ceremony 2007.

Rodong Sinmun on Fundamental Principle to Be Adhered to in Socialist Construction
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, November 8 (KCNA) -- It is a fundamental principle to be consistently adhered to in socialist construction to firmly protect and fully meet the desire for independence and interests of the popular masses. Rodong Sinmun Thursday says this in a signed article. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 In order to build socialism in line with the above-said desire and interests, it is necessary, first of all, to strengthen the working-class party organizationally and ideologically and fully ensure the party leadership over the revolution and construction. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It is also necessary to steadily increase the function and role of the socialist power and protect and develop the socialist ownership. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It is one of the fundamental principles to be consistently maintained in socialist construction to resolutely struggle against imperialism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Abandoning the above-said principle means surrender and betrayal. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Eastern European countries, which were once engaged in building socialism, opted to make concessions over the socialist principle, wavering before the temporary difficulties and yielding to the pressure of the imperialists because they lacked faith in socialism and a firm revolutionary stand. They weakened the leadership role of the ruling parties and uniform leadership function of the socialist states, neglecting the work for strengthening the working-class parties. They, at the same time, compromised with the imperialists without principle, applying the relations of capitalist ownership and capitalist methods of managing economy. This brought such miserable consequences as degenerating socialism and ousting the working-class parties from power and pushing socialism to a collapse in the end. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The historical experience goes to clearly prove that if a country makes a single concession and backdown over the socialist principle, it is bound to make them a hundred times and this will lead to the final collapse of the working-class party and socialism.

Anniversary of Kim Jong Il's Work Observed
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, November 8 (KCNA) -- Rodong Sinmun today dedicates a by-lined article to the 30th anniversary of Kim Jong Il's famous work "On Establishing Revolutionary Trait in Carrying out Party Policies." &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The ideas and theories expounded in the work serve as priceless guidelines in the struggle of the party organizations of different levels and officials and party members and other working people for the implementation of the party policies over the last three decades, says the article. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It goes on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The wise leadership provided by Kim Jong Il to help all party members establish a revolutionary trait of unconditionally carrying out the party policies found its manifestation in that he always saw to it that the education in party policies was steadily intensified among the officials and party members. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 It is a revolutionary leadership principle consistently adhered to by Kim Jong Il to give definite precedence to the ideological and political work in all work. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Under the leadership of Kim Jong Il, the party organizations have dynamically conducted the ideological education to bring home to the officials and party members the party line and policies including the line of socialist economic construction in the Songun era and the policy of agricultural revolution and the policy of light industrial revolution. Many effective styles and methods were created in the education in the party policies. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The wise leadership of Kim Jong Il also found its expression in that he has led the party organizations to closely link the work of organizing and guiding the party life with the implementation of their revolutionary tasks and set an example of the times in devotedly carrying out the party policies and helped all the officials and party members earnestly follow it. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Kim Jong Il created the revolutionary soldier spirit during the difficult period of the "Arduous March" and led all the party members and other people to actively follow the fighting spirit and work style of the People's Army. This marked a landmark occasion in making the spirit of carrying out the party policies in a do-or-die spirit prevail throughout the party.

Book Praising Kim Jong Il Published in S. Korea
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, November 8 (KCNA) -- A book "Kim Jong Il, chairman of the National Defence Commission, and north Korea in 21st century" praising the greatness of Kim Jong Il recently came off the press in south Korea, according to a press report. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The book was edited by the "South Korean Institute for Civil Rights Studies" under the Solidarity for Implementing the South-North Joint Declaration" and released by the "June 15 Publishing House".&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The book having four chapters deals in detail with Kim Jong Il's political and economic lines, leadership mode and policies for national reunification and foreign relations.

National Independence Called for in S. Korea
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, November 8 (KCNA) -- The south Korean Youth and Students Solidarity for Implementing the June 15 Joint Declaration reportedly issued a statement calling upon the youth and students to take the lead in the struggle against the U.S. and for national independence on Nov. 3, 78 years since the Kwangju Students Incident. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The statement noted that the movement of students in Kwangju on Nov. 3, 1929, was a historic great event as it was developed into to the anti-Japanese movement of Korean students, arousing the protest against the Japanese imperialists in the country. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Many years have passed since then, but the Korean people are always exposed to the threat of war with their sovereignty being violated still under the domination of outsiders, it deplored. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The statement said that to inherit the spirit of the Kwangju students movement is just to drive the U.S. forces out of south Korea as soon as possible and gratify the people's desire to lead a free life. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Nobody can break the south Korean people's will to build a new society, the statement said, stressing the need to achieve the independent reunification, peace and prosperity, the cherished desire of the nation, under the banner of the June 15 joint declaration.

Kim Jong Il presencia funcion de XXXI Festival Artistico de Militares 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, 8 de noviembre (ATCC) -- El Dirigente Kim Jong Il, Secretario General del Partido del Trabajo de Corea, Presidente del Comite de Defensa Nacional de la Republica Popular Democratica de Corea y Comandante Supremo del Ejercito Popular de Corea vio la funcion de los militares de las companias de las Unidades no. 682 y no. 3993 del EPC que participan en el XXXI Festival Artistico de Militares del EPC. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Le acompanaron el general de ejercito del EPC Hyon Chol Hae, el teniente general Jong Thae Gun y otros miembros directivos del ejercito. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Los ejecutantes pusieron en la escena el coro "El General se encuentra siempre junto con los soldados", la narracion y cancion "Es buena la vida de la compania", el acordeon y cancion "Vino un acordeonista", el solo "Anoramos al general", Jotae (una especie de flauta) y duo "No llores, Ulnam", el coro "Seremos el septimo regimiento de hoy" y otras variadas piezas. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  A traves de la funcion los militares de las companias cantaron bien el invencible poderio del heroico EPC y la feliz vida de servicio militar llena de optimismo y jubilo. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Al ver la funcion vigorosa e impetuosa, el Dirigente expreso gran satisfaccion de que ellos hicieron una magnifica funcion perfecta en lo ideo-artistico, evaluo de alto el exito de su funcion y les dio agradecimiento. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Todos los militares de Corea crecieron como los uniformados fuertes en la idea y conviccion preparados tanto en lo ideo-politico como en lo militar-tecnico, y dotados de alta preparacion cultural, dijo el y senalo que en el mundo no hay nadie capaz de vencer la fuerza de tal ejercito que se lanza sin vacilacion contra marea y fuego para el partido y el Lider, la patria y el pueblo. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Apunto que el XXXI Festival Artistico de Militares del EPC demuestra plenamente la justeza y vitalidad de la orientacion del partido en materia de cultura y arte de popularizar el arte, y la orgullosa cultura del Songun (priorizacion militar). &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
    La cultura de los militares creada en el ejercito popular refleja el espiritu de la epoca y se colma de optimismo combativo y rico sentimiento, senalo el Comandante Supremo y subrayo que esto sirve de modelo de la vida cultural socialista de la epoca del Songun, de ejemplo autentico que deben seguir todos los funcionarios y otros trabajadores. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
  Destaco que librar con vigor las actividades artisticas revolucionarias en el ejercito es un poderoso medio para elevar la combatividad de la unidad e indico las tareas programaticas que sirven de guia para desarrollar las actividades artisticas masivas.

Regresa a Pyongyang el premier Kim Yong Il
